				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">There could be hundreds of tiles on screen, so checking each tile's bounding box is impractical. You need a system which can quickly determine a collision with a tile <em>and</em> determine where the colliding object should end up, given the original coordinates of the object and the coordinates it would be at had there been no collision.</div>

